text: Yahya Qasim Sare'e (Arabic: يَحْيَى سَرِيعٌ) is a brigadier general and military spokesperson for the Houthi movement supported Yemeni Armed Forces, which is currently engaged in the Red Sea Crisis. == Related pages == *Abdul- Malik al-Houthi ==References== Category:Yemeni people Category:Living people Category:1970 births
title: Yahya Saree
